span>\n                                                        <span>2026-07-17 16:43</span>\n                                                    </p>\n                                                </div>\n        \n                                <section>\n                                                <pre>①在SK海力士股价大幅回调之际，SK集团会长崔泰源周五下场投喂“定心丸”；\n                                    ②他表示，鉴于市场对存储芯片的需求将持续下去，SK海力士股价长期来看将呈上升趋势，并呼吁投资者坚守持仓；\n                                    ③他还表示，AI现在就像个4岁的小孩，要长成大人，必然离不开内存。</pre>\n                                            </section>\n        \n                                <div>\n                                    <div>\n                                        <p>97.3w+ 阅读</p>\n                                            <div data-href=\"https://sj.qq.com/appdetail/com.lanjinger.choiassociatedpress\" data-openapplink=\"cailianpressopen://open?articleid=2429565&articletype=ordinary\">\n                                                \n                                                    <p>17</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div data-href=\"https://sj.qq.com/appdetail/com.lanjinger.choiassociatedpress\" data-openapplink=\"cailianpressopen://open?articleid=2429565&articletype=ordinary\">\n                                                \n                                                    <p>317</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div data-id=\"2429565\">\n                                            <p>展开</p>\n                                            \n                                        </div>\n                                    <div data-id=\"2429565\">\n                                            <p>收起</p>\n                                            \n                                        </div>\n                                </div>\n             